Story VHYEAUq0l AC-1

Implemented hosted resume validation and incremental replay:
- Added HostedMaterializationResumeCursor to the shared hosted materialization contract.
- LocalEngine now validates hosted checkpoints against stream status, manifest root, and anchor replay presence.
- The hosted protocol exposes resume_materialization and rejects tampered checkpoints as invalid requests.
- Remote and transit-client tests cover post-checkpoint replay windows and tampered checkpoint rejection.
